<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-blue);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Landscaping &amp; External Works</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Boundaries &amp; Features</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Boundaries and external features across London and the South East — walls, fencing and gates, railings and balustrades, kerbing and edgings, street furniture and external lighting. The features that define the site edge and finish the public realm, built to BS 1722 fencing and BS 8500 concrete and coordinated as the final external package.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Boundaries &amp; Features →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Boundaries &amp; Features,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Walls, fencing &amp; gates</li><li>Railings &amp; balustrades</li><li>Kerbing &amp; edgings</li><li>Street furniture &amp; external lighting</li><li>Foundations &amp; post setting</li><li>Access gates &amp; controlled entry</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>BS 1722 — fences (fencing systems)</li><li>BS 8500 — concrete specification</li><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>What boundary and feature works do you self-deliver?</summary><p>Walls, fencing and gates, railings and balustrades, kerbing and edgings, plus street furniture and external lighting — installed by our own teams to BS 1722 for fencing systems, on foundations and post settings built to last.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you install gates, railings and balustrades for security and edge protection?</summary><p>Yes. We install fencing, gates, railings and balustrades for boundary security and edge protection — including controlled-entry and access gates — coordinated with the surfacing and lighting so the whole edge is delivered together.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you deliver kerbing, street furniture and lighting as one package?</summary><p>Yes. Kerbing and edgings, street furniture and external lighting are delivered alongside the walls and fencing as the final external package — one accountable team finishing the public realm, not separate trades to coordinate.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Landscaping &amp; External Works</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/">Landscaping &amp; Exte